# Embed source files for tools/internal/aiskill must stay LF in the working
# tree so the //go:embed bytes are deterministic across platforms. Tests
# assert specific byte prefixes (e.g. "---\nname: dcs-sms\n") that break if
# git's autocrlf flips them to CRLF on Windows checkouts.
tools/internal/aiskill/source/*.md text eol=lf
tools/internal/aiskill/source/*.toml text eol=lf
